org.jerkar.api.depmanagement

Class JkMavenPublication

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jerkar.api.depmanagement.JkMavenPublication
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class JkMavenPublication
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Publication specific information to include in POM file in order to be published of a Maven repository. These information contains :
    • The artifacts to be published (main artifact and artifacts with classifiers)
    • Information about describing the project as some public repositories require
    See Also:
